## Reusable Superpowers

A **Mixin** is a standalone chunk of code that you can inject into ANY class, regardless of what its parent is!

```dart
// We write the ability ONCE
mixin CanFly {
  void fly() => print('Whoosh! Im flying!');
}
```
It's not a blueprint for an object. It's just a superpower waiting to be assigned.

## Using `with`

To inject a mixin into a class, we use the `with` keyword alongside our normal `extends`.

```dart
// Normal Inheritance + Superpower Injection!
class Bird extends Animal with CanFly {
}

class Airplane extends Vehicle with CanFly {
}
```
Now, both `Bird` and `Airplane` have the `fly()` method, without copying any code!

